# EchoVault

EchoVault is an intelligent file version tracking system designed for developers, writers, and teams who need a smarter way to manage file history.

Unlike traditional version control tools, EchoVault automatically monitors selected folders, creates AI-generated summaries of changes, and enables natural language search across historical versions.

## Features

* Automatic file change detection
* AI-generated version summaries
* Natural language search
* Fast local storage
* Cross-platform support (Windows, Linux, macOS)
* One-click file recovery
* Lightweight and privacy-focused
# TraceNest

TraceNest is a lightweight and intelligent file monitoring system designed for developers, teams, and power users.

## Features

* Real-time folder monitoring
* Automatic file change tracking
* Duplicate file detection using hash comparison
* Activity timeline generation
* Export reports to JSON and CSV
* Cross-platform support (Windows, Linux, macOS)
* Simple REST API for integrations
* Modern command-line interface

## Use Cases

* Monitor project directories
* Track document modifications
* Detect unwanted file changes
* Organize storage and remove duplicates
* Generate audit reports for teams

## Tech Stack

* Python 3.12+
* FastAPI
* SQLite
* Watchdog
* Pandas

## Future Roadmap

* Web dashboard
* AI-powered anomaly detection
* Cloud synchronization
* Team collaboration features

